18
00:00:51,340 --> 00:00:54,310
but where do we start?

19
00:00:54,310 --> 00:00:57,030
We start by ensuring that
our website is responsive.

20
00:00:57,030 --> 00:01:00,660
If a user visits our web page
on a desktop or a mobile device,

21
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:04,818
they need to have the
same positive experience.

22
00:01:04,818 --> 00:01:07,420
If you would like to learn
